items.label: What is Trok dog?
items.content: Inspired by the concept of Shiba Inu, Trok is also a meme coin in dogs where we aim to build a thriving community. We strive to create a robust ecosystem that fosters connectivity and growth.

items.label: What is $TROK token ?
items.content: $TROK is a brc20 coin issued on Bitcoin blockchain, the total supply is 210,000,000,000. The half of them will issue with a low price, so user will got the tokens without gas war on brc20 mint process.

items.label: Can I got $TROK rewards?
items.content: Yes, We will provide token rewards to individuals who contribute to our community, We welcome your suggestions and feedback.

items.label: Do your launchpad offer refunds?
items.content: If the funding does not meet the expected goal, we will issue refunds.
